title: GTA 5 Roleplay - SURVIVING TINY $1,000,000 BOUNTY | RedlineRP
author: Treyten
description:
That was crazy...
Today I became tiny again, but this time I set a $1Million dollar bounty on myself and needed to survive it. A lot of people tried to claim the money and I had a ton of crazy escapes. The cops ended up coming too and it was pretty insane. There are a lot of funny moments in this GTA 5 episode, enjoy!
